      <title>华尔街银行预测中国将迎来十年来最大幅度降息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-06/wall-street-banks-predict-biggest-china-rate-cuts-in-a-decade</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一些华尔街银行人士认为，随着政策制定者加大力度刺激增长、抑制通货紧缩，中国央行明年将进行十年来最大幅度的降息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-06/wall-street-banks-predict-biggest-china-rate-cuts-in-a-decade</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 06 Dec 2024 00:59:38 GMT</pubDate>
